<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mining Solutions & Transportation Work</title>

  <!-- css file link  -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/media.css">

  <!-- bootstrap cdn link  -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- remix icon cdn  -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  
  <!-- font family use  -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
</head>
<body >
  <%- include('nav.ejs') %>
<main>
    <article>
        <section class="py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <!-- Heading -->
                <div class="row mb-5">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">Mining Solutions</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted">
                    Our Mining Solutions service is designed to provide end-to-end support for every aspect of mining operations. 
                    From exploration and extraction to processing, logistics, and sustainability, we ensure maximum efficiency, 
                    safety, and long-term value creation. With advanced equipment and highly skilled professionals, we help 
                    industries extract valuable resources responsibly while reducing environmental impact.
                    </p>
                </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Content with Image -->
                <div class="row align-items-center p-justify mb-5">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <figure>
                        <img src="/img/Mining and Extraction.jpg" alt="Mining Operations" class="img-fluid rounded shadow w-100" height="auto">
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Comprehensive Exploration</h2>
                    <p>
                    We use modern technologies such as geological surveys, 3D mapping, and advanced drilling 
                    techniques to identify and evaluate mineral-rich zones. Our exploration team ensures precise 
                    planning, reducing costs and optimizing time. By adopting sustainable exploration methods, 
                    we minimize disruption to local ecosystems while ensuring resource accuracy for future development.
                    </p>
                </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Second Content Block -->
                <div class="row p-justify align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse mb-5">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <figure>
                             <img src="img/Mining.jpg" alt="Mining Equipment" class="img-fluid rounded shadow w-100" height="auto">
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Efficient Extraction</h2>
                    <p>
                    Our mining solutions prioritize efficient and safe extraction of minerals. By integrating 
                    cutting-edge machinery and skilled manpower, we maximize yield while minimizing waste. 
                    Strict safety protocols and compliance with industry standards guarantee secure working conditions. 
                    We are committed to responsible mining practices that respect both human safety and environmental balance.
                    </p>
                </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Third Content Block -->
                <div class="row p-justify align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <figure>
                    <img src="/img/Processing and Grading.jpg" alt="Processing Facility" class="img-fluid rounded shadow w-100" height="auto">
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Processing & Refinement</h2>
                    <p>
                    After extraction, our advanced processing facilities ensure that raw materials are refined 
                    with precision and quality control. We implement eco-friendly techniques to reduce 
                    water and energy consumption while maintaining high production output. This guarantees 
                    that industries receive pure, high-quality resources ready for manufacturing and industrial use.
                    </p>
                </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Fourth Content Block -->
                <div class="row p-justify align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <figure>
                    <img src="/img/Sustainability and Innovation.png" alt="Sustainable Mining" class="img-fluid rounded shadow w-100" height="auto">
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Sustainability & Innovation</h2>
                    <p>
                    We believe in building a sustainable future by adopting green mining practices, reducing carbon emissions, 
                    and rehabilitating mined areas. Through constant innovation, we integrate AI-driven monitoring, automated 
                    equipment, and IoT-based safety solutions. Our Mining Solutions not only drive business growth but also 
                    contribute to long-term environmental preservation.
                    </p>
                </div>
                </div>

                <!-- New Content: Transportation -->
                <div class="row p-justify align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <figure>
                    <img src="img/Transportation & Logistics.jpg" alt="Mining Transportation" class="img-fluid rounded shadow w-100" height="auto">
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Transportation & Logistics</h2>
                    <p>
                    We provide integrated logistics solutions for the safe and timely transportation of extracted minerals. 
                    With a strong network of trucks, railway freight, and port facilities, we ensure hassle-free 
                    delivery of raw materials to processing plants and end-users. Our fleet management system 
                    ensures cost-effectiveness and real-time tracking.
                    </p>
                </div>
                </div>

                <!-- New Content: Safety -->
                <div class="row p-justify align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <figure>
                    <img src="img/Health & Safety Standards.jpg" alt="Safety in Mining" class="img-fluid rounded shadow w-100" height="auto">
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Health & Safety Standards</h2>
                    <p>
                    Safety is our highest priority. We strictly follow international safety standards 
                    to protect workers, equipment, and the environment. Regular training programs, 
                    protective gear, and advanced monitoring systems reduce risks and ensure smooth operations. 
                    Our zero-compromise policy has made us one of the most trusted partners in the mining sector.
                    </p>
                </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</main>
<%- include('footer.ejs') %>
  <!-- bootstrap js -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
